Description: Fun, Flirty and bold V-neck style dress. This dress has a rouched waist and flirty chiffon skirt. The straps have fully beaded accenting to add a touch of glam. Comes in two colors (Sunshine and Pistachio)
Simple yet elegant strapless chiffon dress, complete with a geometical waist line accent.
Simple yet elegant strapless taffeta dress, complete with a floral waist line accent.
Headturning strapless belted little red satin dress!
Strapless chiffon overlay dress with beaded bodice. The cut-outs expose a fully beaded peek-a-boo accent!

Girly, flowy, Strapless chiffon dress rouched to one side connecting a rose style accent. The satin belt accentuates your waist while you dance the night away. 6 Colors! (Truffle, Peacock, Watermeleon, Sage, Navy, Teal/peacock, Coral)
Strapless, Mermaid cocktail dress with black accenting
Fully bedazzled strapless bodice! Turn heads with this multi-layered skirt dress.
Stunning plum rouched cocktail dress with asymmetrical design to show off your curves. The back of the dress is mostly see through mesh that connects to the beaded assymetrical belt!
Playful taffeta dress with V-neckline showcasing a rouched waist with floral accent
Fully bedazzled, off shoulder, one sleeve dress! Beautiful detail on mesh sleeve to give that floating gem appearance! Two colors
Playful scoop neck chiffon dress with rouched waistline to show off your curves. Two colors (burnt orange and Sangria)
Fully rouched strapless cocktail dress with belted accent! Two colors (Black and Red)
Flirty strapless dress with rouched bodice and muli-layered chiffon skirt. Three colors (Purple, Black, and Coral)

Mermiad inspired mint hi-lo dress! The strapless corset style bodice wiht lace up back is completely encrusted with gems to steal the show.
Breathtaking fully bedazzled, strapless corset style bodice with toole skirt.

Mermaid inspired! Strapless, sweetheart neckline with FULL sequin skirt.

Showstopping little black dress! Strapless (can be converted with clip on straps)
Beautiful take on "The little black dress". Fully beaded halter style bust and form fitting skirt makes this the perfect dress for any occasion!
Jaw-dropping cocktail dress with fully see-through back accented with floral design. The front bodice is fully bedazzled with sequins.
Elegant short dress with mint blue overlay and scalloped bottom.
Steal the show with the geometrically beaded bodice with cutouts to show off your waistline. The two-tone ribbon skirt makes this the ultimate party dress. Two colors (pool, pink)
This two-piece ensamble is sure to turn heads with it's fully beaded halter style top and matching beaded belt sewn onto the skirt!
Vibrant multicolored dress with shallow V-neckline and stunning midriff cutoutt making this a playfully elegant piece.
PINK PINK PINK! BarbieCore cocktail dress! Fully beaded bodice with mesh see-through bust. Back has a cropped style design with zip enclosure. (skirt is satin)
Elegant and Romantic black and gold cocktail dress that gives you that hourglass shape.
Stand out with this Bollywood themed two piece set! The top is fully beaded with a sheer nude mesh fabric in front. The skirt has a matching beaded belt swen into the satin skirt.
Sleeping beauty inspired dress with fully beaded bodice and zip enclosure

This halter style little black dress is sure to fit any occassion with its beaded waist and peek-a-boo bust.
Turn heads with this little red dress. The plunging V-neck is offset with a sheer red mesh completing this fully beaded bodice and satin skirt.
Fairy inspired accenting covers the bust while matching teal/green mesh covers the bodice leading into a flirty chiffon skirt.
This cinderella inspired dress has a bold sequin design on the bodice with accenting gems.
Sweet and Sophisticated! This dress has a tight fitted V-neck top with spaghetti straps and a flirty flowy skirt.
Turn heads with this little red dress. The plunging V-neck is offset with a sheer red mesh completing this fully beaded bodice and satin skirt.
This stunning red satin halter and floral dress is sure to turn heads with this innocent flirty feel.
Two piece halter syle, peek-a-boo top and matching chiffon skirt. The skirt has a satin sewn on belt while the top has a lace overlay look perfect for any occasion.

Elegant halter syle dress with side cutouts. The front of the bodice is encrusted with gems to give it that regal look. The front connects by mesh fabric to give a barely there illusion. This dress also has pockets trimmed with matching gems.
Fully beaded halter style bodice with see through black mesh to give that peek-a-boo look. The skirt portion of the dress is multi-layered giving this piece a flirty feel.
Red cocktail dress with plunging neckline! Beautiful red and white encrusted gems sewn onto see-through mesh highlighting the waistline. Perfect for any special occasion.
Stunning emerald green strapless cocktail dress with corset style lace up back
